Collaborate with Dashboard Annotations

Annotate dashboard widgets with comments posted in the dashboard and in Chatter. With annotations, you can hold conversations about your data and how itâ€™s visualized.

To annotate: 
Use CRM Analytics.
Select Annotate from the dropdown menu on any dashboard widget.
Click the speech bubble icon to open the Annotations panel.

Annotations are saved as open or resolved. Detached annotations remain visible when a widget is deleted.

You can @mention anyone in your org, but security setup controls access to the dashboard. Images and screenshots may be visible to users without access to the dashboard.

CRM Analytics dashboard annotations are integrated with Chatter.
Comments appear as Chatter posts, allowing colleagues to respond and view the annotated dashboard with applied filters.
Annotations can be resolved or deleted from the dropdown menu.
